"ngram\": \"women'sfootballsquads\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Olympics\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB has not sent a men's football squad to the Paris Olympics due to fears harboured byScotland,WalesandNorthern Irelandthat playing as a single entity - Great Britain - could risk their future ability to compete independently at other international tournaments.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.056784613191509e-14, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a men's football squad\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"fears\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"byScotland\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"WalesandNorthern Irelandthat\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"a single entity\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"their future ability\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"other international tournaments\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Olympics, which are governed by the International Olympic Committee (IOC), the four home nations would have to enter one combined team, as Team GB does for all other sports, rather than competing separately as they do inFifaorUefacompetitions.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.056784613191509e-14, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_Olympic_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the four home nations\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"one combined team\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"all other sports\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"inFifaorUefacompetitions\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as the worries around affecting each country's standing in football outside the Olympics, there is also the issue presented by four different football associations having to decide on one team to represent them all - which undoubtedly would have risked some heated discussions.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each country's standing\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"four different football associations\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"one team\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"some heated discussions\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB's absence fromParis 2024is nothing unusual, though, as Britain have not sent a men's football team to an Olympic Games on foreign soil since 1960.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"en